Limit the grant of honoraria not to exceed 25% of their basic salary.

Stop providing the JOs with overtime pay since they are not among those authorized to render overtime services with pay per existing rules and regulations;

Evaluate the work efficiency of every Job Order assigned at the BAC Office.  Require them to maximize available working hours and practice efficiency and time management in the performance of their functions; and

Investigate and look into the deficiencies noted in the recording of daily time records.

The Local Finance Committee shall critically determine income from local sources that are reasonably realizable and attainable;

Conduct  regular monitoring of collections against targets;

Take measures to improve the collection efficiency of the City;

Revisit the Tax Ordinance for possible updates and provide better or additional provisions for its effective and efficient implementation; and

Get more familiar with the new chart of accounts and harmonize the process or system of recording between the accounting and Budget section.

